OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FITV News, which has been reporting on
OL,7,Fthe devastating effects of Blast
OL,8,FInduced Traumatic Brain Injury on
OL,9,Fveterans and their families, has
OL,10,Ftested the pressure wave that
OL,11,Fscientists now believe is damaging
OL,12,Fsoldiers' brains. ITV News Science
OL,13,FCorrespondent Martin Stew has this
OL,14,Fspecial report
OL,16,FWords by ITV Senior News Editor, Paul
OL,17,FTyson
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FFrom a red metal box, Trevor Lawrence
OL,7,Fpicks out a lump of what looks like
OL,8,Fplasticine, the shape and size of a
OL,9,Ftennis ball.
OL,11,FTwo hundred grams of military-grade
OL,12,Fplastic explosive, on its own
OL,13,Frelatively safe, but with a detonator
OL,14,Finserted, the charge is lethal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FTo place the detonator, Trevor works
OL,7,Falone, limiting the risk of accident
OL,8,Fto just one man. A former British Army
OL,9,Fbomb disposal officer who served
OL,10,Fseveral tours of Northern Ireland and
OL,11,Fled de-mining work in Iraq, Trevor is
OL,12,Fused to this lonely walk.
OL,14,FJob done, he takes position in the
OL,15,Fcontrol tower and detonates the
OL,16,Fcharge. Even behind thick concrete
OL,17,Fwalls we can feel the blast as a dull
OL,18,Fthud in the chest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FBy military standards the explosion is
OL,7,Fsmall, about the size of a hand
OL,8,Fgrenade, but it is powerful enough to
OL,9,Fcreate the phenomenon that we have
OL,10,Fcome to see.
OL,12,FTrevor's team at Cranfield
OL,13,FUniversity's explosive test centre on
OL,14,FSalisbury Plain have installed high
OL,15,Fspeed cameras around the range.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FIn super slow motion, they clearly
OL,7,Fshow the primary blast wave, a
OL,8,Fhemispheric wall of energy moving
OL,9,Foutwards from the seat of the
OL,10,Fexplosion at the speed of sound,
OL,11,Fcompressing the air in front to create
OL,12,Fa pulse of overpressure.
OL,14,FIt is this pressure wave that
OL,15,Fscientists now believe is damaging
OL,16,Fsoldiers' brains, even when they fire
OL,17,Ftheir own weapons in training.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FProfessor Ben Dunkley, who has studied
OL,7,Fblast exposure in Canadian soldiers
OL,8,Fand veterans, explained: "That shock
OL,9,Fwave is hitting the body and then that
OL,10,Fenergy is being transmitted into the
OL,11,Fbrain and it's just like being shaken
OL,12,Faround.
OL,14,F"It can cause shearing damage, injure
OL,15,Fthe cells and over time they can
OL,16,Fdegenerate and die off."
OL,18,FNow, for the first time, Nato has
OL,19,Fissued guidance to member states on
OL,20,Fhow much blast overpressure troops
OL,21,Fshould be exposed to in training.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FFor the UK, where there are currently
OL,7,Fno restrictions at all and where the
OL,8,Fgovernment treats soldiers' brain
OL,9,Fhealth as an area for research rather
OL,10,Fthan action, the report represents a
OL,11,Fsignificant step.
OL,13,FThe Nato guidance is for armies to
OL,14,Flimit overpressure in training to four
OL,15,Fpounds per square inch (Psi) for a
OL,16,Fsingle exposure and a cumulative daily
OL,17,Ftotal of 32 Psi. The alliance says it
OL,18,Fmay revise these guidelines as the
OL,19,Fscience evolves.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FMr Lawrence told us: "Once upon a time
OL,7,Fwe thought the lowest threshold of
OL,8,Fdamage was to the eardrums but now
OL,9,Fit's becoming apparent that you could
OL,10,Fbe damaged at much lower levels, so
OL,11,Feveryone's different, there really
OL,12,Fisn't, as far as I'm concerned, a safe
OL,13,Flevel - it varies from person to
OL,14,Fperson."
OL,16,FBut blast exposures can be hard to
OL,17,Fpredict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FOverpressure can be reflected back by
OL,7,Fwalls, hard floors or vehicles so that
OL,8,Fa weapons user in a confined space can
OL,9,Fbe hit with several times the effect
OL,10,Fas one in the open.
OL,12,FFew people would stand five metres
OL,13,Ffrom the blast of a 500g lump of
OL,14,Fplastic explosive - the minimum safety
OL,15,Fdistance is 100 metres - yet our
OL,16,Fmonitors showed a similar overpressure
OL,17,Ffrom this explosion to that produced
OL,18,Fby firing the standard British Army
OL,19,Fmortar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FWe halved the distance and tried a
OL,7,Fsmaller 200g charge elevated to waist
OL,8,Fheight - again, no-one in their right
OL,9,Fmind would stand this close. Our
OL,10,Fmonitors showed an overpressure wave
OL,11,Fof six psi - the same as firing an AT4
OL,12,Fshoulder-held anti-tank weapon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FThese figures come from American
OL,7,Fresearch into the blast overpressure
OL,8,Fexposure to soldiers firing heavy
OL,9,Fweapons. A Freedom of Information Act
OL,10,Frequest by ITV News shows the Ministry
OL,11,Fof Defence has never monitored any
OL,12,FBritish weapons systems for blast
OL,13,Foverpressure in connection with brain
OL,14,Fhealth.
OL,16,FThe effects of this repeated exposure
OL,17,Fare very real.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FITV News has been reporting on the
OL,7,Fdevastating effects of Blast Induced
OL,8,FTraumatic Brain Injury on veterans and
OL,9,Ftheir families. Symptoms include
OL,10,Femotional problems, severe headaches,
OL,11,Fsleep loss and short-term memory
OL,12,Fissues.
OL,14,FBrain fog, sensitivity to noise and
OL,15,Flight, dizziness and balance problems
OL,16,Fare also common.
OL,18,FAn almost total lack of awareness in
OL,19,Fthe NHS means veterans affected are
OL,20,Froutinely misdiagnosed, usually with
OL,21,Fpsychiatric conditions like PTSD.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,7,Faffected by this issue or has a story
OL,8,Fto share, you can get in touch by
OL,9,Femailing: yourstory@itv.com
OL,11,FNobody knows how many veterans are
OL,12,Faffected, likely thousands. There are
OL,13,Fwell-documented links to family
OL,14,Fbreakup, contact with the criminal
OL,15,Fjustice system, homelessness and
OL,16,Fsuicide and a significantly higher
OL,17,Frisk of neurodegenerative disease in
OL,18,Flater life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FHigh explosive is the currency of
OL,7,Fmodern conflict. In the First World
OL,8,FWar more soldiers were killed by
OL,9,Fartillery than machine gun. Since then
OL,10,Fthe ratio has only risen - a recent
OL,11,Fstudy from the war in Ukraine showed
OL,12,F2% of casualties were hit by bullets,
OL,13,Fthe others all came from the effects
OL,14,Fof high explosive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,FIf they are to fight effectively
OL,7,Fsoldiers must train, which means they
OL,8,Fmust be familiar with their weapon
OL,9,Fsystems and the effects of high
OL,10,Fexplosive. But by limiting that
OL,11,Fexposure in training NATO are
OL,12,Fsignalling that member states can and
OL,13,Fshould act to prevent long-term
OL,14,Fneurological damage to their service
OL,15,Fmembers and veterans.
OL,17,FThe Ministry of Defence told ITV News:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,F"The long-term effects of blast
OL,7,Fexposure on the brain are now able to
OL,8,Fbe scientifically investigated in ways
OL,9,Fnot previously available thanks to
OL,10,Fadvances in the fields of neuroimaging
OL,11,Fand neuroscience.
OL,13,F"Causation has not yet been shown and
OL,14,Fis the subject of this ongoing
OL,15,Fresearch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784911675
OL,3,CITV News tests hidden force of
OL,4,Cmilitary blast linked to brain injuries
OL,6,F"Defence has invested #3.5m in a
OL,7,Fworld's first mobile quantum-enabled
OL,8,Fbrain lab which will deploy this year
OL,9,Fand test the effects of blast exposure
OL,10,Fin relation to brain health on
OL,11,Fmilitary personnel."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
